This vagrant settings is intended to compile EiffelStudio in a Virtual Machine.

 - Eiffel installed in unix layout  (i.e  /usr/bin/estudio ...)
 - It also creates an account "eiffel" (password is "eiffel") under /home/eiffel


Howto:

- Install VirtualBox 4.2
- Install vagrant from http://vagrantup.com/

Use vagrant to download and configure everything

  git clone https://github.com/jocelyn/vagrant_scripts
  cd eiffelstudio_ppa/precise64_vbox 
  vagrant up

note: you can also checkout using svn, instead of using git
  svn checkout https://github.com/jocelyn/vagrant_scripts/tree/master/eiffelstudio_ppa/precise64_vbox eiffelstudio_precise64_vbox
  cd eiffelstudio_precise64_vbox
  vagrant up
  
For now, this will configure a linux x64 virtualbox machine, install EiffelStudio from PPA on it.
